Generate IDs

Source: R/generate_tables.R
generate_tables.Rd

Generate IDs

Usage

generate_tables(
  annotations = NULL,
  file_negative = NULL,
  file_positive = NULL,
  min_confidence = 0.4,
  show_example = FALSE,
  export_csv = TRUE,
  export_html = TRUE,
  export_dir = "data/processed",
  export_name = "cascade_table"
)

Arguments

annotations

Annotations

file_negative

File negative

file_positive

File positive

min_confidence

Min confidence

show_example

Show example? Default to FALSE

export_csv

Export CSV

export_html

Export HTML

export_dir

Export Dir

export_name

Export name

Value

Tables

Examples

if (FALSE) { # \dontrun{
generate_tables()
} # }
